{"text_id":114459,"tokens":["How"," to"," Treat"," Childhood"," Neph","ro","tic"," Syndrome","\n\n","Childhood"," nephro","tic"," syndrome"," is"," a"," condition"," in"," which"," the"," kidneys"," suddenly"," begin"," to"," leak"," large"," amounts"," of"," protein"," into"," the"," urine","."," This"," can"," cause"," a"," range"," of"," symptoms",","," including"," swelling",","," weight"," gain",","," and"," fatigue","."," If"," your"," child"," has"," been"," diagnosed"," with"," childhood"," nephro","tic"," syndrome",","," there"," are"," several"," steps"," you"," can"," take"," to"," help"," manage"," the"," condition"," and"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," complications",".","\n\n","**","Do"," Active"," Home"," Monitoring","**","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," important"," things"," you"," can"," do"," to"," help"," your"," child"," manage"," childhood"," nephro","tic"," syndrome"," is"," to"," do"," active"," home"," monitoring","."," This"," means"," keeping"," track"," of"," your"," child","'","s"," urine"," protein"," levels",","," blood"," pressure",","," and"," weight"," on"," a"," regular"," basis","."," You"," can"," use"," a"," home"," urine"," test"," kit"," to"," check"," for"," protein"," in"," your"," child","'","s"," urine",","," and"," you"," should"," also"," keep"," track"," of"," any"," medications"," your"," child"," is"," taking"," and"," any"," changes"," in"," their"," symptoms",".","\n\n","**","Have"," Your"," Child"," Take"," Pred","nis","one","**","\n\n","The"," first"," line"," of"," treatment"," for"," childhood"," nephro","tic"," syndrome"," is"," usually"," pred","nis","one",","," a"," steroid"," medication","."," Pred","nis","one"," can"," help"," reduce"," the"," amount"," of"," protein"," in"," your"," child","'","s"," urine"," and"," relieve"," symptoms"," such"," as"," swelling","."," However",","," it"," can"," also"," have"," side"," effects"," such"," as"," mood"," swings",","," insomnia",","," and"," weight"," gain",".","\n\n","**","Look"," into"," Cal","cine","urin"," Inhibitors","**","\n\n","If"," your"," child","'","s"," symptoms"," do"," not"," respond"," to"," pred","nis","one",","," their"," doctor"," may"," recommend"," a"," cal","cine","urin"," inhibitor"," such"," as"," cyclo","spor","ine"," or"," tac","ro","limus","."," These"," medications"," can"," help"," reduce"," the"," immune"," system","'","s"," response"," and"," reduce"," protein","uria",".","\n\n","**","Talk"," to"," Your"," Doctor"," about"," Myco","phen","olate"," M","ofe","til"," (","MM","F",")**","\n\n","My","co","phen","olate"," m","ofe","til"," (","MM","F",")"," is"," another"," medication"," that"," may"," be"," recommended"," for"," children"," with"," nephro","tic"," syndrome","."," MM","F"," works"," by"," reducing"," the"," immune"," system","'","s"," response"," and"," can"," be"," effective"," in"," reducing"," protein","uria",".","\n\n","**","Consider"," Starting"," on"," an"," Alk","yl","ating"," Agents","**","\n\n","Alk","yl","ating"," agents"," such"," as"," cyclo","phosp","ham","ide"," may"," be"," recommended"," for"," children"," who"," have"," severe"," or"," resistant"," nephro","tic"," syndrome","."," These"," medications"," can"," help"," reduce"," the"," immune"," system","'","s"," response"," and"," reduce"," protein","uria",","," but"," they"," can"," also"," have"," serious"," side"," effects"," such"," as"," hair"," loss"," and"," increased"," risk"," of"," infection",".","\n\n","**","Know"," that"," Most"," Patients"," Rel","apse","**","\n\n","Unfortunately",","," most"," children"," with"," nephro","tic"," syndrome"," will"," experience"," a"," relapse"," at"," some"," point","."," This"," means"," that"," their"," symptoms"," will"," return",","," and"," they"," may"," need"," to"," restart"," treatment","."," It","'","s"," important"," to"," work"," closely"," with"," your"," child","'","s"," doctor"," to"," develop"," a"," treatment"," plan"," that"," can"," help"," manage"," rela","pses",".","\n\n","**","Work"," to"," Minimize"," Potential"," Complications","**","\n\n","Children"," with"," nephro","tic"," syndrome"," are"," at"," risk"," for"," a"," range"," of"," complications",","," including"," infections",","," blood"," clots",","," and"," kidney"," damage","."," It","'","s"," important"," to"," work"," closely"," with"," your"," child","'","s"," doctor"," to"," minimize"," the"," risk"," of"," these"," complications",".","\n\n","**","Tack","le"," E","dema"," by"," Drinking"," Less"," Water","**","\n\n","E","dema",","," or"," swelling",","," is"," a"," common"," symptom"," of"," nephro","tic"," syndrome","."," One"," way"," to"," help"," manage"," edema"," is"," to"," reduce"," your"," child","'","s"," fluid"," intake","."," Encourage"," your"," child"," to"," drink"," plenty"," of"," water",","," but"," avoid"," excessive"," fluid"," intake",".","\n\n","**","Limit"," Your"," Child","'","s"," Salt"," Intake","**","\n\n","Sodium"," can"," exacerbate"," edema",","," so"," it","'","s"," a"," good"," idea"," to"," limit"," your"," child","'","s"," salt"," intake","."," Encourage"," your"," child"," to"," eat"," a"," low","-","sodium"," diet"," and"," avoid"," processed"," foods",".","\n\n","**","Care","fully"," Consider"," Taking"," Di","ure","tics","**","\n\n","Di","ure","tics"," can"," help"," reduce"," edema"," by"," increasing"," urine"," production","."," However",","," they"," can"," also"," have"," side"," effects"," such"," as"," dehydration"," and"," electrolyte"," imbalances",".","\n\n","**","Consider"," Water"," Pills"," and"," Other"," Stronger"," Di","ure","tics","**","\n\n","If"," your"," child","'","s"," edema"," is"," severe",","," their"," doctor"," may"," recommend"," water"," pills"," or"," other"," stronger"," diure","tics","."," These"," medications"," can"," help"," reduce"," edema",","," but"," they"," can"," also"," have"," serious"," side"," effects"," such"," as"," dehydration"," and"," electrolyte"," imbalances",".","\n\n","**","Talk"," to"," Your"," Doctor"," about"," Getting"," Album","in","**","\n\n","Album","in"," is"," a"," protein"," that"," can"," help"," reduce"," edema","."," Your"," child","'","s"," doctor"," may"," recommend"," infusions"," of"," albumin"," to"," help"," manage"," edema",".","\n\n","**","Consider"," the"," Head","-","Out","-","of","-","Water"," Immersion"," Technique","**","\n\n","The"," head","-","out","-","of","-","water"," immersion"," technique"," involves"," submer","ging"," your"," child","'","s"," body"," in"," water"," up"," to"," their"," neck","."," This"," can"," help"," reduce"," edema"," by"," increasing"," blood"," flow"," and"," reducing"," fluid"," in"," the"," legs",".","\n\n","**","Eat"," Health","ily","**","\n\n","Eating"," a"," healthy"," diet"," can"," help"," your"," child"," manage"," their"," symptoms"," and"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," complications","."," Encourage"," your"," child"," to"," eat"," plenty"," of"," fruits",","," vegetables",","," and"," whole"," grains",".","\n\n","**","Start"," an"," Exercise"," Program","**","\n\n","Regular"," exercise"," can"," help"," your"," child"," manage"," their"," symptoms"," and"," reduce"," the"," risk"," of"," complications","."," Encourage"," your"," child"," to"," engage"," in"," low","-","impact"," activities"," such"," as"," walking"," or"," swimming",".","\n\n","**","Expect"," Swelling","**","\n\n","S","welling"," is"," a"," common"," symptom"," of"," nephro","tic"," syndrome",","," and"," it"," may"," take"," some"," time"," to"," resolve","."," Be"," patient"," and"," work"," closely"," with"," your"," child","'","s"," doctor"," to"," manage"," swelling",".","\n\n","**","Keep"," an"," Eye"," on"," Your"," Child","'","s"," Cholesterol","**","\n\n","Children"," with"," nephro","tic"," syndrome"," are"," at"," risk"," for"," high"," cholesterol",","," which"," can"," increase"," the"," risk"," of"," heart"," disease","."," Make"," sure"," your"," child","'","s"," doctor"," monitors"," their"," cholesterol"," levels"," regularly",".","\n\n"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}